Package: iivw
Title: Inverse Intensity and Visit Weighting for Longitudinal Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-03-15
Authors@R: person("Timothy P", "Copeland", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "timothy.copeland@ki.se",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2801-7928"))
Description: Implements inverse intensity weighting (IIW), inverse probability
    of treatment weighting (IPTW), and their combination (FIPTIW) for
    longitudinal studies with irregular visit patterns. IIW corrects for
    outcome-dependent visit frequency using Andersen-Gill counting-process
    Cox models (Buzkova & Lumley 2007). IPTW corrects for treatment
    confounding via propensity scores. FIPTIW combines both corrections
    (Tompkins, Dubin & Wallace 2025). Provides weight computation and
    weighted outcome model fitting with GEE or mixed model estimation.
